The Nigeria Police Force on Thursday placed N10 million reward for anybody who provides useful information on two suspected criminals.  
The Police in a tweet on Thursday, requested citizens to report to the nearest station whenever they have any detailed information that could lead to the arrest of the wanted suspects.
The Force Public Relations Officer (FPRO), Forced Headquarters, Abuja, Frank Mba, distributed a flier showing the individuals as captured on CCTV at a crime scene.
The Police appealed to anyone with credible knowledge about the whereabouts of the individuals to report to a police station or call 08034377912 or 08036064791.
